:1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ec791d6402c6eaec2eebe96cc01ecdfb74981695","tid":1115561,"uid":81113,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:36:57.000Z","msg":"咁沙膽，敢整list追擊，小心連登護主厹報復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:01:57.000Z","msg":"一個都未蒲頭喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:04:01.000Z","msg":"瞓左冇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:11:01.000Z","msg":"印度、南韓、沙特打壓女權，<br />\nWhitegy話 &ldquo;人微言輕&rdquo; 兼 &ldquo;忙到甩轆&rdquo;，所以要出街遊行，不了。<br />\n<br />\n但係呂麗瑤生按白做，妄告教練，告唔入，<br />\n香港嘅女權婦團突然唔覺得自己 &ldquo;人微言輕&rdquo;，突然唔再 &ldquo;忙到甩轆&rdquo; 喎 ... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港女權婦團係乜德性，係乜嘴臉，明啦下話。<br />\n<br />\n兩個字：無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff981ecd9b41ebbcd9885bff64b74a04e981377","tid":1115561,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:20:19.000Z","msg":"In Pictures: &lsquo;A long way to go&rsquo; &ndash; over 100 people march in Hong Kong&rsquo;s annual SlutWalk against sexual assault<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3 December 2018 </span>15:50<br />\nJennifer Creery<br />\n<br />\nCrowds marched in Central on Sunday under the slogan &ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>My body, my choice</strong></span>,&rdquo; to protest against sexual violence and victim blaming as part of Hong Kong&rsquo;s 7th annual SlutWalk.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來已經係香港第7次 slut walk<br />\n<br />\n上一次係2018年12月，係威係勢。<br />\n<br />\n沙特打壓卡農同著草香港兩姊妹呢？<br />\n仲乜野由2019年由1月到而家4月，大拿拿4個月時間，總共成120日，一次slut walk都唔搞呀？<br />\n<br />\n又話 &ldquo;My body, my choice&rdquo;<br />\n乜原來沙特女人嘅身體，係無自主權力嘅咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd3ae9b94d109a5812eeded1e39ce685c2ff04e","tid":1115561,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/47683616_10155783824225785_1429989733202657280_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F47683616_10155783824225785_1429989733202657280_n.jpg&h=d6afe269&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n認清楚班人嘅嘴臉喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港女權婦團 = 假道學假仁假義偽君子"},{"pid":"fe44bec1f957dd131a6ce025807182807a3d6e70","tid":1115561,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:30:18.000Z","msg":"香港男孩女孩於升中試，點樣排位，一定出聲，因為有著數，話男女平等。<br />\n<br />\n公司機構嘅高層同中層員工，女性員工人數有幾多，一定要出聲，因為有著數，話男女平等。<br />\n（前線勞工要搬搬抬抬，就永遠唔會出聲，話要增加女性員工數目）<br />\n<br />\n英式法治制度之下，有著數，出聲爭取，好安全。就算爭取失敗到好，有法治保護，唔會槍斃，唔會斬首。<br />\n<br />\n沙特女人爭取女權？<br />\n佢死佢賤，唔關我事。<br />\n<br />\n嗱，睇清楚班人嘅嘴臉。<br />\n兩個字：無恥"},{"pid":"95aa25f233464b21890fe93738fbc4cc358c9143","tid":1115561,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:31: